Experiment 1 Results (v1.0 + v1.1)

Feb 3, 2021

Feb 3 Update

  • Spell checking and lemmatization when classifying response types
  • RT computed by time to first type

Exclusions

  • Excluding 5 participants who gave an incorrect resonse on more than half of trials, leaving 28 participants in the analysis.
  • Dropping 24 trials with reaction times over more than 3 sds above the mean (more than 19.4 seconds), leaving 536 trials in the analysis.

Typing time

We didn’t enforce a time limit on word entry. It looks like most people aren’t abusing it horribly.

But they are more likely to take a long time typing on error trials.
